text:
<@U02N38PCBEF> I'm happy to share tips! If your open rates are 55% but reply rate is only 3% it's most likely a problem of targeting and personalization.

Usually we are getting open rate of around 70% and reply rate of 20%+ using cold email + LinkedIn messages. I have actually written some articles about this, so if you're interested or have any questions just shoot me a DM and I'm happy to help.
